Global Ozone Generating Device Market Insights
Ozone Generating Device Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Ozone Generating Device Market Overview
The ozone generating device market was valued at approximately USD 1.7 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 2.6 billion by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 7.1% from 2025 to 2030. The increasing demand for water and air purification technologies, coupled with growing awareness of environmental concerns, is driving the expansion of this market. Ozone generators are used across multiple industries such as healthcare, food processing, and water treatment, where their ability to disinfect and remove pollutants is crucial. The surge in industrial applications of ozone generators is expected to fuel market growth, making it a key segment within the environmental and industrial technology sectors.

